<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="sk">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Dvedeci — Vinotéka & Vínny bar Bratislava</title>
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Cormorant+Garamond:ital,wght@0,300;0,400;0,600;1,300;1,400&family=DM+Sans:wght@300;400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
*, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

:root {
  --cream: #F5EFE3;
  --cream-dark: #EDE0CC;
  --burgundy: #8B1A2E;
  --burgundy-light: #A82238;
  --dark: #1C0F0A;
  --dark-warm: #150C08;
  --text-dark: #2C1A0E;
  --text-muted: #8A7060;
  --gold: #C4933A;
  --font-serif: 'Cormorant Garamond', Georgia, serif;
  --font-sans: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
}

html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }
body { font-family: var(--font-sans); background: var(--cream); color: var(--text-dark); overflow-x: hidden; }

/* ── NAV ── */
nav {
  position: fixed; top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; z-index: 100;
  height: 72px; padding: 0 48px;
  display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between;
  transition: background 0.4s ease, backdrop-filter 0.4s ease;
}
nav.scrolled {
  background: rgba(28, 15, 10, 0.93);
  backdrop-filter: blur(14px);
}
.nav-logo {
  font-family: var(--font-serif); font-size: 22px; font-weight: 600;
  letter-spacing: 0.08em; text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--cream); text-decoration: none;
}
.nav-links { display: flex; gap: 40px; list-style: none; }
.nav-links a {
  font-family: var(--font-sans); font-size: 12px; font-weight: 400;
  letter-spacing: 0.15em; text-transform: uppercase;
  color: rgba(245,239,227,0.65); text-decoration: none;
  transition: color 0.2s; cursor: pointer;
}
.nav-links a:hover { color: var(--cream); }

/* ── HERO ── */
#hero {
  position: relative; height: 100vh; min-height: 700px;
  display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center;
  justify-content: center; overflow: hidden; background: var(--dark);
}
.hero-bg {
  position: absolute; inset: 0;
  background-image: url('119040662_3279857868762387_3412981304177771717_n.jpg');
  background-size: cover; background-position: center 30%;
  opacity: 0.5; filter: sepia(0.25);
}
.hero-overlay {
  position: absolute; inset: 0;
  background: linear-gradient(to bottom, rgba(28,15,10,0.35) 0%, rgba(28,15,10,0.1) 45%, rgba(28,15,10,0.88) 100%);
}
.hero-content {
  position: relative; z-index: 2; text-align: center; padding: 0 24px;
  opacity: 0; animation: fadeUp 1s ease 0.3s forwards;
}
.hero-eyebrow {
  font-family: var(--font-sans); font-size: 11px; font-weight: 400;
  letter-spacing: 0.3em; text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--gold); margin-bottom: 20px;
}
.hero-title {
  font-family: var(--font-serif);
  font-size: clamp(80px, 13vw, 160px);
  font-weight: 300; line-height: 0.9; letter-spacing: -0.01em;
  color: var(--cream);
}
.hero-hours {
  position: absolute; bottom: 48px; left: 56px; z-index: 2;
  opacity: 0; animation: fadeUp 0.8s ease 0.8s forwards;
}
.hours-grid {
  display: grid; grid-template-columns: auto auto; gap: 5px 40px;
}
.h-day {
  font-family: var(--font-sans); font-size: 10px; font-weight: 400;
  letter-spacing: 0.2em; text-transform: uppercase;
  color: rgba(245,239,227,0.4);
}
.h-time {
  font-family: var(--font-serif); font-size: 13px; font-weight: 300;
  letter-spacing: 0.06em; color: rgba(245,239,227,0.7);
}
.h-time.closed { color: var(--burgundy-light); font-style: italic; }

@keyframes fadeUp {
  from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(24px); }
  to   { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
}

/* ── SHARED ── */
.section-label {
  font-family: var(--font-sans); font-size: 10px; font-weight: 400;
  letter-spacing: 0.3em; text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--text-muted); margin-bottom: 20px;
}
.section-label-light {
  font-family: var(--font-sans); font-size: 10px; font-weight: 400;
  letter-spacing: 0.3em; text-transform: uppercase;
  color: rgba(245,239,227,0.3); margin-bottom: 20px;
}
.btn {
  display: inline-block; font-family: var(--font-sans); font-size: 11px;
  font-weight: 500; letter-spacing: 0.2em; text-transform: uppercase;
  text-decoration: none; padding: 14px 36px; cursor: pointer;
  border: 1px solid var(--burgundy); color: var(--burgundy);
  background: transparent; transition: background 0.25s, color 0.25s;
}
.btn:hover { background: var(--burgundy); color: var(--cream); }
.btn-light {
  border-color: rgba(245,239,227,0.5); color: var(--cream);
}
.btn-light:hover { background: var(--cream); color: var(--dark); }

/* ── VINO FILOZOFIA ── */
#vino {
  background: var(--cream); padding: 120px 0; overflow: hidden;
}
.vino-inner {
  max-width: 1200px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 48px;
  display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 80px; align-items: start;
}
.vino-text { padding-top: 32px; }
.section-heading {
  font-family: var(--font-serif);
  font-size: clamp(44px, 5vw, 72px);
  font-weight: 300; line-height: 1.05; color: var(--text-dark);
  margin-bottom: 28px;
}
.section-heading em { font-style: italic; color: var(--burgundy); }
.section-heading-light {
  font-family: var(--font-serif);
  font-size: clamp(44px, 5vw, 72px);
  font-weight: 300; line-height: 1.05; color: var(--cream);
  margin-bottom: 28px;
}
.section-heading-light em { font-style: italic; color: var(--gold); }
.body-text {
  font-size: 15px; font-weight: 300; line-height: 1.85;
  color: #5C4A38; margin-bottom: 44px;
}
.body-text-light {
  font-size: 15px; font-weight: 300; line-height: 1.85;
  color: rgba(245,239,227,0.55); margin-bottom: 44px;
}
.body-text p + p { margin-top: 14px; }

/* vino photos */
.vino-photos {
  display: grid; grid-template-rows: 340px 200px; gap: 16px;
}
.photo-full { overflow: hidden; }
.photo-full img { width:100%; height:100%; object-fit:cover; display:block; transition: transform 0.6s ease; }
.photo-full:hover img { transform: scale(1.03); }
.photo-row { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 16px; }
.photo-half { overflow: hidden; }
.photo-half img { width:100%; height:100%; object-fit:cover; display:block; transition: transform 0.6s ease; }
.photo-half:hover img { transform: scale(1.04); }

/* ── VINO VYBER (dark) ── */
#vino-vyber {
  background: var(--dark-warm); padding: 120px 0; overflow: hidden;
}
.vyber-inner {
  max-width: 1200px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 48px;
  display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1.2fr; gap: 80px; align-items: center;
}
.vyber-text { padding-top: 0; }
.vyber-photos {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
  grid-template-rows: 300px 260px;
  gap: 16px;
}
.vyber-photo-main {
  grid-column: span 2; overflow: hidden;
}
.vyber-photo-main img { width:100%; height:100%; object-fit:cover; display:block; filter: brightness(0.85); transition: transform 0.6s, filter 0.4s; }
.vyber-photo-main:hover img { transform: scale(1.03); filter: brightness(1); }
.vyber-photo-sm { overflow: hidden; }
.vyber-photo-sm img { width:100%; height:100%; object-fit:cover; display:block; filter: brightness(0.8); transition: transform 0.6s, filter 0.4s; }
.vyber-photo-sm:hover img { transform: scale(1.04); filter: brightness(1); }

/* ── JEDLO ── */
#jedlo {
  background: var(--cream); padding: 120px 0; overflow: hidden;
}
.jedlo-inner {
  max-width: 1200px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 48px;
  display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 80px; align-items: start;
}
.jedlo-photos {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
  grid-template-rows: 260px 260px;
  gap: 16px;
}
.jedlo-photo-wide {
  grid-column: span 2; overflow: hidden;
}
.jedlo-photo-wide img { width:100%; height:100%; object-fit:cover; display:block; transition: transform 0.6s; }
.jedlo-photo-wide:hover img { transform: scale(1.03); }
.jedlo-photo { overflow: hidden; }
.jedlo-photo img { width:100%; height:100%; object-fit:cover; display:block; transition: transform 0.6s; }
.jedlo-photo:hover img { transform: scale(1.04); }

/* ── DVOJDECOVY EVENT (dark) ── */
#event {
  background: var(--dark); padding: 120px 0; overflow: hidden;
}
.event-inner {
  max-width: 1200px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 48px;
  display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 80px; align-items: start;
}
.event-photos {
  display: grid; grid-template-rows: 280px 280px; gap: 16px;
}
.event-photo { overflow: hidden; }
.event-photo img { width:100%; height:100%; object-fit:cover; display:block; filter: brightness(0.85) saturate(0.9); transition: transform 0.6s, filter 0.4s; }
.event-photo:hover img { transform: scale(1.03); filter: brightness(1) saturate(1); }
.event-text { padding-top: 32px; }

/* ── POUKAZKY ── */
#poukazky {
  background: var(--cream-dark); padding: 120px 0; overflow: hidden;
}
.poukazky-inner {
  max-width: 1200px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 48px;
  display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 80px; align-items: start;
}
.poukazky-text { padding-top: 32px; }
.poukazky-photos {
  display: grid; grid-template-rows: 380px 200px; gap: 16px;
}
.poukazky-photo-main { overflow: hidden; }
.poukazky-photo-main img { width:100%; height:100%; object-fit:cover; display:block; transition: transform 0.6s; }
.poukazky-photo-main:hover img { transform: scale(1.03); }

/* ── KONTAKT (dark) ── */
#kontakt {
  background: var(--dark); padding: 120px 48px;
}
.kontakt-inner {
  max-width: 1200px; margin: 0 auto;
  display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 80px; align-items: start;
}
.kontakt-left {}
.kontakt-body {
  font-size: 15px; font-weight: 300; line-height: 1.85;
  color: rgba(245,239,227,0.55); margin-bottom: 44px; max-width: 420px;
}
.kontakt-details { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 20px; margin-bottom: 56px; }
.kontakt-item { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 16px; }
.kontakt-icon { width: 18px; height: 18px; flex-shrink: 0; opacity: 0.45; color: var(--cream); }
.kontakt-item-text {
  font-size: 14px; font-weight: 300; color: rgba(245,239,227,0.75);
  text-decoration: none; line-height: 1.5;
}
a.kontakt-item-text:hover { color: var(--cream); }

.kontakt-hours {
  display: grid; grid-template-columns: auto auto; gap: 6px 40px;
}
.kh-day {
  font-family: var(--font-sans); font-size: 11px; font-weight: 400;
  letter-spacing: 0.18em; text-transform: uppercase;
  color: rgba(245,239,227,0.35);
}
.kh-time {
  font-family: var(--font-serif); font-size: 14px; font-weight: 300;
  color: rgba(245,239,227,0.65); letter-spacing: 0.04em;
}
.kh-time.closed { color: var(--burgundy-light); font-style: italic; }

/* kontakt photos */
.kontakt-photos {
  display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; grid-template-rows: 260px 260px; gap: 16px;
}
.kontakt-photo-full { grid-column: span 2; overflow: hidden; }
.kontakt-photo-full img { width:100%; height:100%; object-fit:cover; display:block; filter: brightness(0.8); transition: transform 0.6s, filter 0.4s; }
.kontakt-photo-full:hover img { transform: scale(1.03); filter: brightness(0.95); }
.kontakt-photo { overflow: hidden; }
.kontakt-photo img { width:100%; height:100%; object-fit:cover; display:block; filter: brightness(0.75); transition: transform 0.6s, filter 0.4s; }
.kontakt-photo:hover img { transform: scale(1.04); filter: brightness(0.9); }

/* tagline */
.tagline {
  font-family: var(--font-serif); font-size: clamp(32px, 3.5vw, 52px);
  font-weight: 300; font-style: italic; line-height: 1.1;
  color: rgba(245,239,227,0.2); margin-top: 48px;
}

/* ── FOOTER ── */
footer {
  background: var(--dark-warm); padding: 40px 48px;
  display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between;
  border-top: 1px solid rgba(245,239,227,0.06);
}
.footer-logo {
  font-family: var(--font-serif); font-size: 17px; font-weight: 300;
  letter-spacing: 0.12em; text-transform: uppercase;
  color: rgba(245,239,227,0.25);
}
.footer-copy { font-size: 11px; color: rgba(245,239,227,0.18); }
.footer-addr { font-size: 11px; color: rgba(245,239,227,0.22); text-align: right; line-height: 1.7; }

/* ── RESPONSIVE ── */
@media (max-width: 900px) {
  nav { padding: 0 24px; }
  .nav-links { gap: 24px; }
  .nav-links a { font-size: 11px; }
  .vino-inner, .vyber-inner, .jedlo-inner, .event-inner, .poukazky-inner, .kontakt-inner {
    grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 48px; padding: 0 24px;
  }
  #kontakt { padding: 80px 24px; }
  footer { flex-direction: column; gap: 16px; text-align: center; padding: 32px 24px; }
  .footer-addr { text-align: center; }
  .hero-hours { left: 24px; bottom: 32px; }
}
@media (max-width: 600px) {
  .nav-links { display: none; }
  .vino-photos { grid-template-rows: 260px 160px; }
  .jedlo-photos { grid-template-columns: 1fr; grid-template-rows: repeat(3, 220px); }
  .jedlo-photo-wide { grid-column: span 1; }
  .kontakt-photos { grid-template-columns: 1fr; grid-template-rows: repeat(3, 200px); }
  .kontakt-photo-full { grid-column: span 1; }
  #vino, #vino-vyber, #jedlo, #event, #poukazky { padding: 80px 0; }
}
</style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- NAV -->
<nav id="navbar">
  <a href="#hero" class="nav-logo">Dvedeci</a>
  <ul class="nav-links">
    <li><a href="#vino">Víno</a></li>
    <li><a href="#jedlo">Menu</a></li>
    <li><a href="#event">Dvojdecový Event</a></li>
    <li><a href="#poukazky">Poukážky</a></li>
    <li><a href="#kontakt">Kontakt</a></li>
  </ul>
</nav>

<!-- HERO — fotka 16 -->
<section id="hero">
  <div class="hero-bg"></div>
  <div class="hero-overlay"></div>
  <div class="hero-content">
    <p class="hero-eyebrow">Vinotéka &amp; Vínny bar · Bratislava</p>
    <h1 class="hero-title">Dvedeci</h1>
  </div>
  <div class="hero-hours">
    <div class="hours-grid">
      <span class="h-day">Pondelok</span><span class="h-time">17:30 – 22:00</span>
      <span class="h-day">Utorok</span><span class="h-time">16:00 – 22:00</span>
      <span class="h-day">Streda</span><span class="h-time">16:00 – 22:00</span>
      <span class="h-day">Štvrtok</span><span class="h-time">16:00 – 22:00</span>
      <span class="h-day">Piatok</span><span class="h-time">16:00 – 22:00</span>
      <span class="h-day">Víkend</span><span class="h-time closed">Zatvorené</span>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- VINO FILOZOFIA — fotky 1, 2 -->
<section id="vino">
  <div class="vino-inner">
    <div class="vino-text">
      <p class="section-label">01 — Filozofia</p>
      <h2 class="section-heading">Od vinohradu<br><em>k poháru</em></h2>
      <div class="body-text">
        <p>Každé víno u nás má príbeh. Nevyberáme podľa katalógov ani veľkých mien, hľadáme vinárov, ktorí robia veci po svojom, od vinohradu až po fľašu.</p>
        <p>Slovenské vína z Malých Karpát, Tokaja aj zabudnutých regiónov, a občas niečo zo sveta, čo nás jednoducho zaujalo. Ceníme si remeslo a ľudí za ním. Preto siahame po vínach, kde vieme odkiaľ hrozno pochádza a kto ho zbieral.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="vino-photos">
      <div class="photo-full">
        <img src="119460059_3288136911267816_325507749717504453_n.jpg" alt="Vinár pri práci vo vinograde">
      </div>
      <div class="photo-row">
        <div class="photo-half">
          <img src="119603325_3288136907934483_1335531736851475007_n.jpg" alt="Zber hrozna — ruky s nožnicami">
        </div>
        <div class="photo-half">
          <img src="509360924_9985785938169513_2087286295862396777_n.jpg" alt="Dvedeci kraft štítky na víno">
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- VINO VYBER — fotky 3, 4, 5 -->
<section id="vino-vyber">
  <div class="vyber-inner">
    <div class="vyber-text">
      <p class="section-label-light">01.2 — Výber</p>
      <h2 class="section-heading-light">Výber vín<br><em>nie je veda</em></h2>
      <p class="body-text-light">Je to cit. Buď ťa víno zastaví uprostred rozhovoru, alebo nezastaví. Práve také hľadáme. A keď ho nájdeme, skončí na našich poličkách.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="vyber-photos">
      <div class="vyber-photo-main">
        <img src="602855881_18494150365079745_5363393797691479787_n.jpg" alt="Fľaše vína v taške">
      </div>
      <div class="vyber-photo-sm">
        <img src="602974073_18494150374079745_2527835187552272752_n.jpg" alt="Fľaše vína v debničke">
      </div>
      <div class="vyber-photo-sm">
        <img src="72980108_2496135737134608_897093843499876352_n.jpg" alt="Dezert pri víne">
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- JEDLO — fotky 6, 7, 8 -->
<section id="jedlo">
  <div class="jedlo-inner">
    <div class="jedlo-photos">
      <div class="jedlo-photo-wide">
        <img src="72980108_2496135737134608_897093843499876352_n.jpg" alt="Pečená hruška s medom a orechami">
      </div>
      <div class="jedlo-photo">
        <img src="120184690_3331153506966156_1505425382230825930_n.jpg" alt="Domáce lokše">
      </div>
      <div class="jedlo-photo">
        <img src="475239807_18439558420079745_151426865190703618_n.jpg" alt="Dezert s pohárom červeného vína">
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="jedlo-text" style="padding-top:32px;">
      <p class="section-label">02 — Jedlo</p>
      <h2 class="section-heading">Niečo chutné<br><em>k vínku</em></h2>
      <div class="body-text">
        <p>Víno chutí lepšie s niečím dobrým na tanieri vedľa. Preto dbáme na to, aby bolo z čoho vyberať.</p>
        <p>Čo práve ponúkame, nájdete v našom Menu.</p>
      </div>
      <a href="#" class="btn">Menu</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- DVOJDECOVY EVENT — fotky 9, 10 -->
<section id="event">
  <div class="event-inner">
    <div class="event-text">
      <p class="section-label-light">03 — Udalosti</p>
      <h2 class="section-heading-light">Dvojdecový<br><em>Event</em></h2>
      <div class="body-text-light">
        <p>Každý Dvojdecový Event je iný. Raz špeciality od našich kuchárov, inokedy vzácny hosť za barom alebo pri stole a niekedy všetko naraz.</p>
        <p>Miesta je vždy len toľko, koľko naše stoly a stoličky umožnia. Presné dátumy, program aj to čo bude na tanieri nájdete v sekcii Čo vás čaká. Tí čo sledujú včas, majú zaručenú možnosť si vychutnať Dvojdecový Event.</p>
      </div>
      <a href="#" class="btn btn-light">Čo vás čaká</a>
    </div>
    <div class="event-photos">
      <div class="event-photo">
        <img src="471841342_1102370354914852_1530341951994678796_n.jpg" alt="Grilovaná chobotnica — Dvojdecový Event">
      </div>
      <div class="event-photo">
        <img src="42756682_1893836267364561_6248401388104056832_n.jpg" alt="Špeciality z Dvojdecového eventu">
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- POUKAZKY — fotky 11, 12 -->
<section id="poukazky">
  <div class="poukazky-inner">
    <div class="poukazky-text">
      <p class="section-label">04 — Darčeky</p>
      <h2 class="section-heading">Darčekové<br><em>poukážky</em></h2>
      <div class="body-text">
        <p>Darček nemusí zaberať miesto v skrini. Môže zaberať miesto v pamäti. Napríklad taký príjemný večer s lahodným vínom a dobrou spoločnosťou.</p>
        <p>Práve preto naše Dvedeci poukážky nie sú odveci. Poukážky si môžete kúpiť priamo u nás vo vinotéke alebo online. Po objednaní vám zašleme poukážku na email. Navrhnutá ako skutočný darček — stojí za vytlačenie. Stačí ju však ukázať aj z telefónu.</p>
      </div>
      <a href="#" class="btn">Poukážky</a>
